      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "Arrival times from TWIM experiments are calibrated to experimental CCS values from DTIM platforms (DTCCSN2) using a set of standards.",
      "asbval:note": "Semantic equivalence: MOCCal is designed to convert arrival times to CCS, so pre-calibrated data would not require this step.",
