      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "Experimental data can be imported as a spreadsheet containing feature identifiers along with their corresponding m/z, charge state, retention time, and arrival time values. Based on provided charge states, features with two or more charges will be calibrated with only the peptide z = 2 or z = 3 calibration curves.",
