    {
      "@id": "asbval:assertion/skill/ion-mobility-arrival-time-conversion/004",
      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "MOCCal, or Multi-Omic CCS Calibrator, is a Python application that automates the assignment of unknown features to the power law calibration that provides the most accurate CCS value. MOCCal calibrates every experimental arrival time with up to three class-specific calibration curves",
