      "asbval:evidence_quote": "CCS values, unlike drift times, are comparable across different laboratories and instrumentation... MOCCal utilizes biomolecule-specific TWIM CCS calibration equations based on the power law to generate calibrated CCS values for a molecular feature of unknown identity.",
